snippet.title: Super Crome: Bullet Purgatory EA Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Super Crome Launches into Steam Early Access March 19th!

You can follow and wishlist it here: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/98...

Follow the development on Twitter: 
https://twitter.com/supercromegame

Subscribe to our newsletter:
https://supercro.us18.list-manage.com...

Trailer Music by Jordan Dube:
https://mobile.twitter.com/jordanopoly
